{"sections":{"39f713ce-2be9-44f1-9310-85b9ec69af48":{"type":"three-column","blocks":{"template--16107012980905__39f713ce-2be9-44f1-9310-85b9ec69af48-167962820178899593-0":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Screenshot_2026-03-12_at_1.12.47_PM.png","mobile_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Screenshot_2026-03-12_at_1.12.47_PM.png"}}},"block_order":["template--16107012980905__39f713ce-2be9-44f1-9310-85b9ec69af48-167962820178899593-0"],"settings":{"enable_dark":false,"subheading":"<p><strong>MEET US IN MELBOURNE <\/strong><\/p>","title":"<p>Ceremonial Atelier <\/p>","description":"<p>Our Ceremonial Atelier is all about creating meaningful connections and unforgettable pieces. We’re so excited to be returning to Melbourne for our next Atelier, bringing the world of NMJ beyond our two Sydney showrooms and offering you the chance to connect with our team in person.<\/p><p>Join us at the <strong>Hannah St Hotel <\/strong>on <strong>Sunday 19 April <\/strong>or <strong>Monday 20 April t<\/strong>o explore our Ceremonial and Engagement collections, or begin your bespoke design journey with us.<\/p><p>Whether for a proposal, your wedding day, a sentimental keepsake, or a milestone worth remembering, we would be honoured to work alongside you to bring your dream piece to life.<\/p><p>Spaces are limited — book now to secure your appointment.<\/p>","feature_text":"<p>An exclusive, <em>one-on-one <\/em>design experience beyond our Sydney <em>showrooms.<\/em><\/p>","colour_style":"dark","button_1_metaobject":"","button_1_text":"","button_1_link":"","button_2_metaobject":"booking-melbourne-ceremonial-atelier","button_2_text":"BOOK NOW","button_2_link":"","button_style":"primary"}},"b2f993b2-b2ff-4017-9547-f8bfa906ef33":{"type":"content-list","blocks":{"image_7z4Wkw":{"type":"image","disabled":true,"settings":{"apply_overlay":false,"devices":"mobile_desktop","content_position":"middleLeft","subheading":"<p><strong>JOIN US IN SYDNEY<\/strong><\/p>","title":"","description":"<p>Join us for an intimate 30-minute appointment at a private Sydney residence in the heart of Paddington where you will have the opportunity to collaborate with our expert Bespoke Design Team. Together, we’ll bring your unique vision to life with unparalleled craftsmanship and personalised attention, offering you a glimpse into the creative artistry that defines NMJ.<\/p><p>Our team will be bringing a curated selection of ceremonial and wedding day jewellery. If you have ever dreamed of styling our pieces for your special day, we warmly invite you to join us for a personalised and intimate experience.<\/p>","description_mobile":"<p>Join us for an intimate 30-minute appointment at a private Sydney residence in the heart of Paddington where you will have the opportunity to collaborate with our expert Bespoke Design Team. Together, we’ll bring your unique vision to life with unparalleled craftsmanship and personalised attention, offering you a glimpse into the creative artistry that defines NMJ.<\/p><p>Our team will be bringing a curated selection of ceremonial and wedding day jewellery. If you have ever dreamed of styling our pieces for your special day, we warmly invite you to join us for a personalised and intimate experience.<\/p>","colour_style":"dark","button_1_metaobject":"","button_1_text":"Book Consultation","button_1_link":"https:\/\/nataliemariejewellery.as.me\/schedule\/62dbb371\/appointment\/71380579\/calendar\/any?calendarIds=11135067","button_2_metaobject":"","button_2_text":"","button_2_link":"","button_3_metaobject":"","button_3_text":"","button_3_link":"shopify:\/\/pages\/bespoke-process","button_style":"underline","include_no_media_border":true,"metaobject_autoplay":"","metaobject_loop":"","metaobject_apply_overlay":"","metaobject_content_position":"","metaobject_colour_style":"","metaobject_button_style":"","metaobject_devices":""}}},"block_order":["image_7z4Wkw"],"settings":{"grid_items_count":1,"grid_items_count_pocket":"1\/1","tex